WHY IT'S OPEN

This project was built with AI assistance, and tools like that are trained, in
large part, on creative and constructive work taken without the consent of the
people who made it. If I'm going to accept that help, the least I owe is to
acknowledge it plainly — and to give something back in the same spirit. So this
is open, freely and without request. I know it's ethically gray. I'd rather
stand in it honestly than pretend it's clean. If you build with these tools too,
consider doing the same.

                                                              — Chris Gallegos
